Token.Abstract: NSDictionary+GlucoseConcentrationConversion includes helper methods to converts a glucose concentration values
Converts a glucose value from one unit to another. Available units can be found in UHNBLETypes.h and include kg / L, mol / L, mg / dL and mmol / L.

Parameter.Name: fromUnits
Parameter.Abstract: The units to convert the glucose value from

Parameter.Name: toUnits
Parameter.Abstract: The units to convert the glucose value to

ReturnValue.Abstract: The glucose value for the requested units as a NSNumber
